~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : shutdown                                  ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : shutdown [<secs>/cancel]

   This will shutdown the talker, either immediately or after 
   "secs" seconds.  The cancel option will cancel any timed shutdown.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : reboot
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
